            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Trimmy 0.8.0</h2>
<ul>
<li>Added a menu-only “Paste Reformatted Markdown” action to join wrapped markdown paragraphs and bullet lists while preserving blank lines and fenced code blocks.</li>
<li>Path quoting now only wraps standalone paths (not commands or sentences) when they contain spaces (#17, thanks @n0an).</li>
</ul>
