            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Trimmy 0.6.4</h2>
            <ul>
            <li>Sparkle: auto-download updates when auto-check is enabled, and only show the restart menu entry once an update is ready.</li>
            <li>Command detection: flatten “command + indented args” copies (e.g. emails + flags) into a single pasteable line at Normal aggressiveness; skip transforms for snippets longer than 4 lines.</li>
            <li>Dependencies: refreshed SwiftPM pins (Sparkle 2.8.1, KeyboardShortcuts 1.17.0, MenuBarExtraAccess 1.2.2).</li>
            </ul>
